We will send you an invitation through your calendars for the next Thursday, 14:00 h, universal time coordinated 07:00 h, Pacific time, for a special meeting of staff.
We will take this opportunity to share additional news, answer your questions and spend time connecting with each other.
We're together in this and we're available to help out in the way we can.
